{"tid":2202190,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"香港航空推No Pay Leave Plan. 機師遭減薪六成","createTime":"2020-09-14T11:30:15.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-14T13:52:15.000Z","uid":228995,"like":21,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"d04b880ff2abed92457868ed3cb1ba91c098d4a1","tid":2202190,"uid":228995,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:30:15.000Z","msg":"新冠疫情持續逾半年，航空業大受打擊。《香港01》收到消息，香港航空向全體飛機師發信，將從10月1日起至明年3月31日實行無薪假安排，並減薪多達六成。<br />\n<br />\n《香港01》已經向香港航空查詢，正等待回應。<br />\n<br />\n繼國泰和港龍上周宣布不申請第二輪保就業計劃後，香港航空今日也向飛機師發信，信中表示公司將對所有飛行員實施一個「無薪假方案」（No Pay Leave Scheme），同時亦會減薪及減補貼，無論是機長還是副機師都減六成。相關方案將從10月1日起實行到3月31日。"},{"pid":"2a3a1ac216372b6c072cb2147515d01228120355","tid":2202190,"uid":201604,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"減完都多過你"},{"pid":"5a1aca898548bd770b75d7e394f72cd30d9c2bc0","tid":2202190,"uid":72228,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2a3a1ac216372b6c072cb2147515d01228120355","tid":2202190,"uid":201604,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"減完都多過你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留得職嘅都係有料有經驗<br />\n飛G果班早就準備炒"},{"pid":"c3695041d12ea0adfc3b512f137910dff224577b","tid":2202190,"uid":283557,"like":5,"dislike":2,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"5a1aca898548bd770b75d7e394f72cd30d9c2bc0","tid":2202190,"uid":72228,"like":13,"dislike":2,"score":11,"quote":{"pid":"2a3a1ac216372b6c072cb2147515d01228120355","tid":2202190,"uid":201604,"like":12,"dislike":3,"score":9,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:02.000Z","msg":"減完都多過你"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:31:47.000Z","msg":"呢個真<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n留得職嘅都係有料有經驗<br />\n飛G果班早就準備炒"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-14T11:41:23.000Z","msg":"「留得職嘅都係有料有經驗」<br />\n呢句真係外行得好緊要<br />\n全世界<br />\n都係識人好過識字<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/fac